Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a worker is assigned to a task, 0 otherwise.

Name: assign_story_to_sprint
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a user story is included in a sprint, 0 otherwise.

Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a team is assigned to a project, 0 otherwise.

Name: set_feature_priority
Description: Determines the priority level for a feature.

Name: set_sprint_start_date
Description: The start date for a given sprint.

Name: set_task_status
Description: Sets the status of a task.

Name: set_story_points
Description: Assigns story points to a user story.

Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a worker is assigned to a team, 0 otherwise.

Name: select_feature_for_release
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a feature is included in a release plan, 0 otherwise.

Name: set_worker_availability
Description: Determines the availability percentage for a worker.

Name: set_blocker_status
Description: Sets the status of a blocker.
